{"tid":1605343,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［行動post] 聽日六區出到去做啲咩可以賀佢老母？","createTime":"2019-09-30T09:09:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T09:12:25.000Z","uid":83848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f307684aeba6312b3dc87d8ea8345612ce15bf59","tid":1605343,"uid":83848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T09:09:19.000Z","msg":"聽日中共大壽 <br />\n如果又好似過去三個月咁<br />\n純粹roadblock 對峙 火魔法 根本吸引唔到國際媒體 <br />\n亦到落唔到習維尼面<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: large;\">話左送佢大禮 麻煩大家集思廣益下一齊做啲咩好</span></ins><br />\n<br />\n預左啲狗會清楚 勇武會出黎保護大家<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">拋磚各位和理非不如買哂香港嘅白色蠟燭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽日一齊默站 為我地走左嘅手足哀悼一下</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有興趣傾麻煩幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>最後 <br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n我要真普選！！！<br />\n</strong>"},{"pid":"187aff43b042dd254e3a1edf90c7396dcde9499d","tid":1605343,"uid":83848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T09:09:50.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"6f606481dfe62b7567fc118be7dc161046b54458","tid":1605343,"uid":83848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T09:10:09.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"6d1457031a3964bb7f3633343b414f40664d69c8","tid":1605343,"uid":83848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T09:10:25.000Z","msg":"3/10 不被捕不受傷"},{"pid":"b19f0eaeea0ae4f94fea12e2266f91d4f65e9bc5","tid":1605343,"uid":83848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T09:10:35.000Z","msg":"4/10 和勇不分"},{"pid":"c088babd5cbc2e34c9e93a5ae1d8b531ce1a8a09","tid":1605343,"uid":83848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T09:10:55.000Z","msg":"5/10 兄弟爬山"},{"pid":"2cff222d82cb95917a5b41fe629162e238817961","tid":1605343,"uid":8